data.description: The Colony, in central Murrieta is a 55 and over Senior Community.  It is manicured, guarded 24 hours with a paid security personnel.  The Colony offers a quality, private and quiet living style for its residents.  The 2 bedroom and 1 and .5 bath is an open floor plan home and has it all.  Vaulted ceilings, recessed lighting, accent cabinetry, double mirrored closet doors, fire place, carpeting, epoxy floor in the garage and many other features of this TURNEY home.  The amenities include grand ballroom, library, fitness center, large outdoor pool and many other features including golf on its permisses.  This one will not last long!
